revision.text:
{{DISPLAYTITLE:Plat_DownWaitUpStayLip}} {{Special|206|tag, speed, delay, lip, sound|Platform|DownWaitUpStayLip}} * ''tag'': Tag of affected sector * ''speed'': Speed of move * ''delay'': Tics before going back up. Vanilla Doom lifts waited for 3 seconds, or 105 tics. * ''lip'': Amount of floor to leave showing when platform is lowered * ''sound'': if 0 the platform sound is used, if 1 the moving floor sound is used
Lowers a platform, waits, and then raises it back to its original position. If ''tag'' is 0, then the sector on the line's back side is used.
